data.description: Great opportunity to own this cozy 1 bedroom/1 bath/1 parking with an immediate rental income of $2300/month (tenants contract ends October Oct 11, 2023). Chateau Waikiki is highly desirable and offers 24-hour security, well managed with onsite resident manager, large swimming pool, sun deck, large party rooms with pool table & ping pong, gas BBQ grills, several cabanas surrounded by beautiful landscaping, library and fitness center. Conveniently located just steps from Ala Moana Beach Park, Waikiki, Ala Moana Shopping Center, Hilton Lagoon, Convention Center, Kaka'ako, downtown Honolulu, freeway access, bus stops, shopping, restaurants, and much more! Central AC, washer dryer inside the unit and secured parking. Extra Storage Locker on the same floor. Seller offers $10,000 Closing Cost Credit to Buyer!  Maintenance fees include Central AC, Electricity, Internet, (Hot) Water, Sewer, and Common Areas. VA-approved and pet-friendly to cats and service animals. Tenant occupied unit so showings will only be on appointment.
